ns inside chapter skill approves., **muse** generates concepts; skill positions survivors chapters (muse's dedupe upstream continuity)., **lena** words chapter (voice humanic pass); **weave never wordsmiths.**, **pulse** serializes chapters platform-native content chapter many posts; ledger tracks chapters, posts., **spark's gate** checks arc fit one three references; skill check's engine., **echo** consumes arc investor narrative (pitch-narrative's story brand arc contradict facts, different audience)., **Behavioral Science (when built):** kahneman/cialdini review chapter's framing sits between lena's wording spark's gate.